{"type": "article", "id": 27187, "title": "如果你去墨西哥旅游，不要被这家餐厅的色彩吞没", "description": "用铺天盖地来形容并不为过。\r\n", "date": "2016-05-23T06:53:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27985, "name": "墨西哥餐厅"}, {"id": 5534, "name": "澳大利亚"}, {"id": 27986, "name": "Paco’s Tacos"}, {"id": 27988, "name": "Technē Architecture and Interior Design"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 133, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702151152QfFXOy4WtJaTsZU6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p>对墨西哥菜的印象停留在五彩的配色上，让人联想起那些被五色油彩涂抹的墨西哥小镇，在活泼之中蕴藏着真正的个性和热情。如果提到墨西哥的现代建筑，路易斯·巴拉甘（Luis Barragán）则不得不说，他是普利兹克奖的第二位得主（1980 年），也擅长在墙面使用浓烈的彩色，但往往在简单的几何结构下有一种干净明亮的诗意情绪。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151135pzIXUaOkuqMyTBc6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66631579\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">墨西哥帕丘卡小镇，图片来自 <a href=\"http://y0.ifengimg.com/a/2015_32/b8ed63b356bc511.jpg\">bing</a></p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021511362gezTSNfLQk0FMit.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Fuente de los Amantes，图片来自<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Luis_Barrag%C3%A1n#/media/File:Fuente_de_los_Amantes.JPG\">维基</a></p></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151137lhTQWgM7qp9PcsIC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.26171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Torres_de_Sat%C3%A9lite\" title=\"Torres de Satélite\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Torres de Satélite</a>，图片来自<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ciudad_Sat%C3%A9lite#/media/File:Torres_de_Sat%C3%A9lite_-_2.jpg\">维基</a>\n</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>当墨西哥餐厅 Paco’s Tacos 开到澳大利亚灵伍德（Ringwood）时，建筑事务所<a href=\"http://www.techne.com.au/pacos-tacos-eastland/\">Technē Architecture and Interior Design </a>想起的就是这种彩色的风格。他们在 200 平方米的室内主要使用粉、蓝和黄这三种颜色，墙面、柜台和图画都在这三种颜色的相互撞击中，形成了绚丽活泼的效果。</p>\n<p>黄色的铁制圆拱将房间分割成不同的区间，有趣的是，这些圆拱的大小并不统一，使得这种古典的元素变得跳跃，就像是开放式的露天广场。灯光是沿着圆拱下的柱子设置的，突出了圆拱的线条感，到了晚上，光线就沿着柱子向四周散开，范围并不大，倒是营造了一种静谧的气氛。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151137cVnfEZ2K5qgLoCih.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151140iTwZvdMAGESHBn4l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151141E3ub8C9n4KyYOUBR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021511428audQJxkW9rclMP4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.48809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151143Wa3XxUzHMYOKyNhR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.48809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151145DLuykcTrGnCNxw7v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.48148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151145RsyUbeVjZ0DQMzCc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3568521\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151146pAIb4La0JrB7Tnkg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.48809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">墙面木条的颜色深浅不一，上面的挂饰也很零碎，但在圆拱的对称下依然保持了一种整洁和典雅，在这里吃饭想必能格外放松。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151147xRa3XSPYDTfVoNFB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99009901\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151148tuc0xWOIGfy52SzE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.48809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>当地的建筑师 Ayus Bontanical 设计绿色植物的部分，除了调和颜色外也让环境更有家庭花园的气氛。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021511490Y2DenT5OsIFmd7g.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.48809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151149W4mkZKTMtU5QIhon.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.48809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151150RrlLi40jKZmx61zS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151150j5Wh1BvSoywpt6XY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021511515awL1hqXW7Pzdr49.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/787724/pacos-tacos-techne-architecture-plus-interior-design\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">archdaily</a>、<a href=\"http://www.techne.com.au/pacos-tacos-eastland/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Technē Architecture and Interior Design</a><a href=\"http://www.techne.com.au/pacos-tacos-eastland/\"> </a></p>\n\n"}